{"tid":1039381,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(認真post)我娛樂台Rape God嚴選K-Pop史上頭五位Raper","createTime":"2019-02-27T11:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T05:52:27.000Z","uid":193951,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5a4cdfc94ae35977636a1c902f722ecc2466d40f","tid":1039381,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:16:16.000Z","msg":"第五名:RM<br />\n<br />\n出身自防彈的RM嘅實力一直受到質疑 <br />\n而隨著2018年RM所推出的專輯《mono.》<br />\n這些質疑的聲音亦隨之消失<br />\n相信這個「Rap Monster」為我們帶來更多更好的東西<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cvb76hBX_Oc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCvb76hBX_Oc&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=391fcc09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cvb76hBX_Oc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四名:Zico<br />\n<br />\nZico=創作才子應該沒有人會質疑吧?<br />\n無論身為製作人還是饒舌歌手Zico都是一流的存在<br />\n但他個人的人氣似乎較難帶動他的組合<br />\n因此在本次排行只能屈居第四名<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ewjucLierFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DewjucLierFc&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=3877aa5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ewjucLierFc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三名:T.O.P.<br />\n<br />\nT.O.P.的低音炮饒舌是他的特色所在<br />\n身為天團BIGBANG的其中一員<br />\n他沒有受到組合的音樂所限制<br />\n反而創造出屬於他自己的饒舌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tAoME_aMm1w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtAoME_aMm1w&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=7d46b22b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tAoME_aMm1w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二名:G-Dragon<br />\n<br />\n身為天團BIGBANG的隊長<br />\n他所散發出的光芒遠遠超越其他Idol<br />\n很多人都被G-Dragon的其他才華所吸引<br />\n但他的饒舌遠遠不下於他所擁有的其他才華<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rJnICByeL8Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrJnICByeL8Q&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=0ba383d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rJnICByeL8Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一名:Jackson Wang<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n單係用Rap去界定王嘉爾實在太膚淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身為一個香港人唔單止係K-Pop界發光發熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至要進軍國際嘅舞台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果畀我揀一個最接近神嘅男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰個人一定係王嘉爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S214G1w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS214G1w.gif&h=f4a59186&s={SIZE}\"